(15, 4, 'Is spare parts available? ', '<p>We maintain a considerable collection of genuine spare parts matching different DG models. However, for special parts it is better to notice us earlier. First moving consumable spare parts is readily available but in case of slow moving or special parts , it will little take some time depending on the parts stock availability from manufacturer end.</p>\r\n', '', NULL),
(16, 4, 'What will be the warranty does not cover?', '<p>12 months from the date of delivery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Warranty does not cover:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Defects due to user&rsquo;s improper maintenance.</li>\r\n	<li>All consumable items.</li>\r\n	<li>Diode and surge suppressor failure.</li>\r\n	<li>Normal wear and tear.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Alternations or repairs mot authorized by manufacturer in writing.</p>\r\n', '', NULL),
(17, 4, 'What will be the after sales service (All Parts)?', '<p>After sales service is free for 12 months from the date of commissioning without consumable spare parts.</p>\r\n', '', NULL),
