(20, 4, 'What is the capacity range for excavator? ', '<p>Our excavator covers the capacity which weights from 2.7 Tons to 51 Tons. For bucket capacity its starts from 0.08 cu.m to 4.5 cu.m.</p>\r\n', 'Excavator', NULL),
