(29, 4, 'Is spare parts available for Excavator? ', '<p>We maintain a considerable collection of genuine spare parts matching different excavator models. However, for special parts it is better to notice us earlier. First moving consumable spare parts is readily available but in case of slow moving or special parts, it will little take some time depending on the parts stock availability from manufacturer end.</p>\r\n', 'Excavator', NULL),
(30, 4, 'What will be the warranty (Excavator)?', '<p>Warranty will be provided only for the manufacturer defects supplied Excavator and period will be 12 months or 1500 running hours from the&nbsp; date of commissioning which occurs first, provided that the diesel Excavator will be operated in accordance with our O&amp;M manual and will be maintained in accordance with our overhaul schedule.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Warranty does not cover:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Defects due to user&rsquo;s improper maintenance.</li>\r\n	<li>All consumable items.</li>\r\n	<li>Hose pipe and electrical failure.</li>\r\n	<li>Normal wear and tear.</li>\r\n	<li>Alternations or repairs mot authorized by manufacturer in writing.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'Excavator', NULL),
(31, 4, 'What will be the after sales service( Excavator)?', '<p>After sales service is free for 12 months from the date of commissioning without consumable spare parts.</p>\r\n', 'Excavator', NULL),
