(53, 4, 'What will be the warranty for Wheel loader? ', '<p>Warranty will be provided only for the manufacturer defects supplied Excavator and period will be 12 months or 1500 running hours from the &nbsp;date of commissioning which occurs first, provided that the diesel Excavator will be operated in accordance with our O&amp;M manual and will be maintained in accordance with our overhaul schedule.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Warranty does not cover:&nbsp;<br />\r\n&bull; Defects due to user&rsquo;s improper maintenance. &bull; All consumable items. &bull; Hose pipe and electrical failure.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&bull; Normal wear and tear. &bull; Alternations or repairs mot authorized by manufacturer in writing.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Wheel  Loader', NULL),
