(161, 5, 'Is a dump truck considered heavy equipment?', '<p><strong>Heavy equipment</strong>&nbsp;refers to&nbsp;<strong>heavy</strong>-<strong>duty</strong>&nbsp;vehicles, specially designed for executing construction tasks, most frequently ones involving earthwork operations. They are also known as&nbsp;<strong>heavy</strong>&nbsp;machines,&nbsp;<strong>heavy</strong>&nbsp;trucks, construction&nbsp;<strong>equipment</strong>, engineering&nbsp;<strong>equipment</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>heavy</strong>&nbsp;vehicles, or&nbsp;<strong>heavy</strong>&nbsp;hydraulics</p>\r\n', '', NULL),
(162, 5, 'How much does a bulldozer cost?', '<p>If you need to&nbsp;<strong>rent</strong>&nbsp;a <strong>bulldozer</strong>&nbsp;on a weekly basis, this will cost you around 2.5 Lac (BDT) and the monthly rate for the same&nbsp;<strong>bulldozer</strong>&nbsp;will be around 4 Lac (BDT) .&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', NULL),
